Program: The Documentary
Title: Coronavirus: Questions and answers
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3ct0pf1
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 2 Mar 2020
Are you worried about the Coronavirus? Or do you think that people are worrying too much? In response to concerns about the spread of the virus, we bring together a panel of experts to answer questions from listeners around the world. Image: People line up to buy face masks at a department store in Seoul, South Korea (Credit: Chung Sung-Jun/Getty Images) Show less